To accept this invitation, please register with Patients Know Best using this link: http://pkb-frontend-9/patientPersonalInfoForm.action?uid=2145&temp=5fs85We0qP Questions? 1. Is this medically secure? Patients Know Best is HIPAA-compliant for US patients and Data Protection Act compliant for European ones. The site is part of the UK NHS secure network (N3), so it is already built to NHS security standards and approved for usage with any NHS computer. 2. Do I have to register with the web site? Yes, but registration is free and fast. Please click here: http://pkb-frontend-9/patientPersonalInfoForm.action?uid=2145&temp=5fs85We0qP 3. What happens after I register? You can access the records of Ms AZ Patient 1 to use Patients Know Best together securely. You are receiving this notification because you have been invited as a carer.
